<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>workforest</title>
    <link rel="icon" href="../img/favicon.png">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../css/common.css">
    <script src="../js/jquery-3.7.0.min.js"></script>
    <script src="../js/common.js"></script>
    <script src="../js/stripe-gradient.js"></script>
</head>

<body>
    <canvas id="gradient"></canvas>

    <div class="main-container">
        <header class="custom">
            <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="logo">WORKFOREST</a>
            <div class="search-bar">
                <input type="text" placeholder="Search">
            </div>
            <p class="header-txt">김대덕님, 오늘도 힘차게 화이팅하세요!</p>
            <ul class="wf-util">
                <li>
                    <a href="javascript:void(0)" title="채팅">
                        <i class="xi-wechat"></i>
                    </a>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <a href="javascript:void(0)" title="알림">
                        <i class="xi-bell"></i>
                    </a>
                    <div class="wf-menu-dropdown">
                        <ul class="alarm-list">
                            <li>
                                <img src="/img/icon/avatar.png" class="user-img">
                                <div>
                                    <span class="tit">[일정등록]'주간회의' 일정이
                                        등록되었습니다.</span>
                                    <p>
                                        <span class="date">2024-03-03 11:30</span>
                                        <span class="employee">양연주 사장</span>
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <img src="/img/icon/avatar.png" class="user-img">
                                <div>
                                    <span class="tit">[일정등록]'주간회의' 일정이
                                        등록되었습니다.</span>
                                    <p>
                                        <span class="date">2024-03-03 11:30</span>
                                        <span class="employee">양연주 사장</span>
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <a href="javascript:void(0)" title="설정">
                        <i class="xi-cog"></i>
                    </a>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="user-img-icon" title="사용자">
                        <img src="/img/icon/avatar.png" class="user-img">
                    </a>
                    <div class="wf-menu-dropdown">
                        <div class="wf-flex-box">
                            <img src="/img/icon/avatar.png" class="user-img">
                            <div>
                                <span class="user-info">연구개발본부 개발1팀</span>
                                <span class="user-name">김대덕 사원</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="menu-wrap">
                            <a href="#" class="menu-tit my-profile">내 프로필</a>
                            <a href="#" class="menu-tit logout">로그아웃</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </header>
        <div class="content-wrap">
            <aside class="sidebar custom">
                <div class="sidebar-user-info">
                    <div class="img-box">
                        <img src="/img/icon/avatar.png">
                    </div>
                    <span class="name">김대덕 사원</span>
                    <span class="team">연구개발본부 개발팀</span>
                </div>
                <div id="leftside-navigation" class="leftside-navigation">
                    <ul class="depth1">
                        <li class="sub-menu">
                            <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="arrow">
                                <i class="xi-home"></i>
                                <span>업무관리</span>
                            </a>
                            <ul class="depth2">
                                <li>
                                    <a href="javascript:void(0)">업무</a>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <a href="javascript:void(0)">프로젝트</a>
                                </li>
                            </ul>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                    <ul class="depth1">
                        <li class="sub-menu">
                            <a href="javascript:void(0)">
                                <i class="xi-home"></i>
                                <span>전자결재</span>
                            </a>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                    <ul class="depth1">
                        <li class="sub-menu">
                            <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="arrow">
                                <i class="xi-home"></i>
                                <span>예약/신청</span>
                            </a>
                            <ul class="depth2">
                                <li>
                                    <a href="javascript:void(0)">회의실 예약</a>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <a href="javascript:void(0)">차량 예약</a>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <a href="javascript:void(0)">비품 대여</a>
                                </li>
                            </ul>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                    <ul class="depth1">
                        <li class="sub-menu">
                            <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="arrow">
                                <i class="xi-home"></i>
                                <span>일정관리</span>
                            </a>
                            <ul class="depth2">
                                <li>
                                    <a href="javascript:void(0)">일정</a>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <a href="javascript:void(0)">휴가</a>
                                </li>
                            </ul>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                    <ul class="depth1">
                        <li class="sub-menu">
                            <a href="javascript:void(0)">
                                <i class="xi-home"></i>
                                <span>근태관리</span>
                            </a>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                    <ul class="depth1">
                        <li class="sub-menu">
                            <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="arrow">
                                <i class="xi-home"></i>
                                <span>게시판</span>
                            </a>
                            <ul class="depth2">
                                <li>
                                    <a href="javascript:void(0)">공지사항</a>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <a href="javascript:void(0)">자유게시판</a>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <a href="javascript:void(0)">건의게시판</a>
                                </li>
                            </ul>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                    <ul class="depth1">
                        <li class="sub-menu">
                            <a href="javascript:void(0)">
                                <i class="xi-home"></i>
                                <span>조직도</span>
                            </a>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </aside>

            <main class="custom">
                <!-- =============== body 시작 =============== -->
                <div class="wf-main-container">
                    <!-- =============== 상단타이틀영역 시작 =============== -->
                    <div class="wf-tit-wrap">
                        <h1 class="page-tit">코멘트/댓글</h1>
                        <div class="side-util">
                            <button type="button" class="btn2">등록</button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <!-- =============== 상단타이틀영역 끝 =============== -->
                    <!-- =============== 컨텐츠 영역 시작 =============== -->
                    <div class="wf-content-wrap">

                        <!-- 댓글, 코멘트 영역 시작 -->
                        <div class="comment-area">
                            <ul>
                                <li>
                                    <div class="user-wrap">
                                        <span class="user-thumb">
                                            <img src="/img/icon/avatar.png" alt="예시이미지">
                                        </span>
                                        <div class="user-info">
                                            <div>
                                                <span class="user-name">양연주</span>
                                                <span class="user-position">과장</span>
                                            </div>
                                            <div>
                                                <span class="user-team">개발본부 개발팀</span>
                                                <span class="user-date">2023-05-04 13:20</span>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="user-btn">
                                            <button type="button" class="add-btn"><i class="xi-pen"></i></button>
                                            <button type="button" class="del-btn"><i class="xi-trash"></i></button>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="txt">
                                        wow, amazing 💜
                                    </div>
                                    <button type="button" class="reply-btn">답글</button>
                                </li>
                                <li class="reply">
                                    <div class="user-wrap">
                                        <span class="user-thumb">
                                            <img src="/img/icon/avatar.png" alt="예시이미지">
                                        </span>
                                        <div class="user-info">
                                            <div>
                                                <span class="user-name">양연주</span>
                                                <span class="user-position">과장</span>
                                            </div>
                                            <div>
                                                <span class="user-team">개발본부 개발팀</span>
                                                <span class="user-date">2023-05-04 13:20</span>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="user-btn">
                                            <button type="button" class="add-btn"><i class="xi-pen"></i></button>
                                            <button type="button" class="del-btn"><i class="xi-trash"></i></button>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="txt">
                                        thanks 🤞
                                    </div>
                                    <button type="button" class="reply-btn">답글</button>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <div class="user-wrap">
                                        <span class="user-thumb">
                                            <img src="/img/icon/avatar.png" alt="예시이미지">
                                        </span>
                                        <div class="user-info">
                                            <div>
                                                <span class="user-name">양연주</span>
                                                <span class="user-position">과장</span>
                                            </div>
                                            <div>
                                                <span class="user-team">개발본부 개발팀</span>
                                                <span class="user-date">2023-05-04 13:20</span>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="user-btn">
                                            <button type="button" class="add-btn"><i class="xi-pen"></i></button>
                                            <button type="button" class="del-btn"><i class="xi-trash"></i></button>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="txt">
                                        I don’t think so
                                    </div>
                                    <button type="button" class="reply-btn">답글</button>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <div class="user-wrap">
                                        <span class="user-thumb">
                                            <img src="/img/icon/avatar.png" alt="예시이미지">
                                        </span>
                                        <div class="user-info">
                                            <div>
                                                <span class="user-name">양연주</span>
                                                <span class="user-position">과장</span>
                                            </div>
                                            <div>
                                                <span class="user-team">개발본부 개발팀</span>
                                                <span class="user-date">2023-05-04 13:20</span>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="user-btn">
                                            <button type="button" class="add-btn"><i class="xi-pen"></i></button>
                                            <button type="button" class="del-btn"><i class="xi-trash"></i></button>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="txt">
                                        I think so !
                                    </div>
                                    <button type="button" class="reply-btn">답글</button>
                                </li>
                            </ul>
                            <div class="input-wrap">
                                <span class="user-thumb">
                                    <img src="/img/icon/avatar.png" alt="예시이미지">
                                </span>
                                <input type="text" placeholder="댓글을 입력하세요">
                                <button class="btn4">등록</button>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <!-- 댓글, 코멘트 영역 끝 -->
                    </div>
                    <!-- =============== 컨텐츠 영역 끝 =============== -->
                </div>
                <!-- =============== body 끝 =============== -->
            </main>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>